spec_data.Name: xml-security
spec_data.Description:
The XML Security project is aimed at providing implementation
of security standards for XML. Currently the focus is on the
W3C standards :
- XML-Signature Syntax and Processing; and
- XML Encryption Syntax and Processing.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 04:42:38 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Implementation of W3C security standards for XML
